domain:
(define (domain diarcdomaindomain)
(:requirements :strips :typing :fluents)

(:types
	pogoist_102 - pogoist
	two one - distance
	oak_log - oak_log
	coord distance property - concept
	unlocked - property
	actor physobj - physical
	physical concept - var
	trader_104 trader_103 - trader
	self thief trader pogoist - actor
	open_door oak_log pogo_stick key minecraft_fence diamond_ore plank chest rubber stick block_of_titanium block_of_diamond placeable block_of_platinum diamond crafting_table safe oak_log tree_tap air wall iron_pickaxe breakable door sapling - physobj
	crafting_table plank oak_log sapling tree_tap - placeable
	block_of_platinum diamond_ore plank crafting_table oak_log tree_tap - breakable
	oak_plank - plank
	var - object
)

(:predicates

)

(:functions
	(totalcost)
	(world ?v0)
	(inventory ?v0 ?v1)
	(container ?v0 ?v1)
)

(:action deselect
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - physobj)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor ?obj ) 1)
		(holding ?actor ?obj)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(holding ?actor ?obj))
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
)
(:action trade_1
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 1)
		(increase( inventory ?actor block_of_titanium ) 1)
	)
)
(:action place_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor log two)
		(>=( inventory ?actor tree_tap ) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( world tree_tap ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor log two))
		(facing_obj ?actor tree_tap one)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor tree_tap ) 1)
		(next_to tree_tap oak_log)
	)
)
(:action approach_actor_trader_103_bytwo
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world trader_103 ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
	)
)
(:action approach_actor_trader_104_bytwo
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world trader_104 ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
	)
)
(:action approach_actor_pogoist_102_bytwo
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world pogoist_102 ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(facing_obj ?actor pogoist_102 two)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
	)
)
(:action place_sapling
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(>=( inventory ?actor sapling ) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( world oak_log ) 1)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor sapling ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor air one))
		(facing_obj ?actor log one)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_diamond
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor diamond_ore one)
		(not(floating diamond_ore))
		(holding ?actor iron_pickaxe)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( world diamond_ore ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor diamond_ore one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase( inventory ?actor diamond ) 9)
	)
)
(:action trade_2
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor diamond ) 18)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( inventory ?actor diamond ) 18)
		(increase( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 1)
	)
)
(:action craft_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor plank ) 5)
		(>=( inventory ?actor stick ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( inventory ?actor tree_tap ) 1)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor plank ) 5)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor stick ) 1)
	)
)
(:action collect_from_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(next_to tree_tap oak_log)
		(facing_obj ?actor tree_tap one)
	)
	:effect
		(increase( inventory ?actor rubber ) 1)

)
(:action approach_object_oak_log_bytwo
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world oak_log ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor log two)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_oak_log
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world oak_log ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor log one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_crafting_table
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world crafting_table ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_diamond_ore
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world diamond_ore ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor diamond_ore one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_door
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world door ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor door one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_minecraft_fence
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world minecraft_fence ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor minecraft_fence one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_wall
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world wall ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor wall one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_block_of_platinum
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world block_of_platinum ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor block_of_platinum one)
	)
)
(:action approach_object_chest
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?from_obj - physical ?from_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( world chest ) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?from_obj ?from_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor chest one)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_block_of_platinum
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(floating block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor block_of_platinum one)
		(holding ?actor iron_pickaxe)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( world block_of_platinum ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor block_of_platinum one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 1)
	)
)
(:action collect_from_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor safe one)
		(propertyOf safe unlocked)
		(=( container safe diamond ) 18)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( container safe diamond ) 18)
		(increase( inventory ?actor diamond ) 18)
	)
)
(:action select_iron_pickaxe
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor iron_pickaxe ) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(holding ?actor air))
		(holding ?actor iron_pickaxe)
	)
)
(:action select_key
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor key ) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(holding ?actor air))
		(holding ?actor key)
	)
)
(:action pickup
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - physobj)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one)
		(floating ?obj)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( world ?obj ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase( inventory ?actor ?obj ) 1)
	)
)
(:action craft_stick
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition
		(>=( inventory ?actor plank ) 2)

	:effect (and
		(increase( inventory ?actor stick ) 4)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor plank ) 2)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - breakable)

	:precondition (and
		(not(object ?obj diamond_ore))
		(not(object ?obj block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one)
		(not(floating ?obj))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( world ?obj ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase( inventory ?actor ?obj ) 1)
	)
)
(:action craft_pogo_stick
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor stick ) 2)
		(>=( inventory ?actor rubber ) 1)
		(>=( inventory ?actor block_of_titanium ) 2)
		(>=( inventory ?actor block_of_diamond ) 2)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( inventory ?actor pogo_stick ) 1)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor stick ) 2)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor rubber ) 1)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor block_of_titanium ) 2)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor block_of_diamond ) 2)
	)
)
(:action craft_plank
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition
		(>=( inventory ?actor oak_log ) 1)

	:effect (and
		(increase( inventory ?actor oak_plank ) 4)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor oak_log ) 1)
	)
)
(:action get_sapling
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?facing_obj - physical ?facing_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(=( world oak_log ) 0)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase( inventory ?actor sapling ) 1)
	)
)
(:action trade_0
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 2)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( inventory ?actor block_of_platinum ) 2)
		(increase( inventory ?actor diamond ) 9)
	)
)
(:action trade_3
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor oak_log ) 10)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( inventory ?actor oak_log ) 10)
		(increase( inventory ?actor block_of_titanium ) 1)
	)
)
(:action craft_block_of_diamond
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(>=( inventory ?actor diamond ) 9)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( inventory ?actor block_of_diamond ) 1)
		(decrease( inventory ?actor diamond ) 9)
	)
)
(:action find_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?facing_obj - physical ?facing_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(object ?actor self)
		(=( world safe ) 0)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist)
		(holding ?actor air)
		(>=( inventory ?actor key ) 1)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase( world safe ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
)
(:action open_door
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor door one)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( world door ) 1)
		(increase( world open_door ) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor door one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
	)
)
(:action use_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor safe one)
		(holding ?actor key)
	)
	:effect
		(propertyOf safe unlocked)

)
(:action collect_from_chest
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor chest one)
		(holding ?actor air)
		(=( container chest key ) 1)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease( container chest key ) 1)
		(increase( inventory ?actor key ) 1)
		(not(holding ?actor air))
		(holding ?actor key)
	)
)
)
